snippet.title: Kimberly Flower
snippet.description:
Hello Friends,
This channel is dedicated to talking about all things true crime and skincare.
A little about me, I am an  ex-professional. I decided to quit and move to Los Angeles, CA. In need to talk, teach, share and learn about true crime and skincare, my YouTube channel was created.. Hope you enjoy!

Hope you have a fabulous day and I love you to death 😊

Xoxoxo,
Kim
